            <div type="edition" xml:space="preserve"><head>Text</head><ab><lb n="1"/>
                Homo bonus infas adque <note>sic</note> amicus omnibus <lb n="2"/>hic conquiescit anima superis tradita <lb n="3"/>qui acc<supplied reason="lost">e</supplied>ptum lumen mense XI reddidit <lb n="4"/>Amymone <expan><abbr>e</abbr><ex>x</ex></expan><certainty match="preceding-sibling::node()" locus="value"/> matre e<expan><ex>x</ex><abbr>q</abbr><ex>ue</ex></expan><certainty match="preceding-sibling::node()" locus="value"/> Marcello patre <lb n="5"/>natus Quirina Athenodorus Roma domo
            </ab></div>
            <div type="commentary">
                <p>(B): Z. 4: Die Auflösungen in &amp;quot;&amp;quot;Amymone ē matre ēq. Marcello&amp;quot;&amp;quot; sind unklar: Gordon 1929-1944: Ē = est/et?, Ē(t) Q(uinto); AE 1947: Ē MATRE Ē Q MARCELLO; Gordon 1947, AE 1948: ē matre ē(que) Marcello.</p>
            </div>
